When using 'Quality Transmutation', for Butterflies, you will ONLY get modifiers marked $.
They can be gotten with 'Normal Transmutation' as well, but the chances are lower with more options.

* Brainy Glasses (#10005)
    View User HP: 0

* Parme's Glasses (#10015)
    View User HP: 0

* Irmin's Glasses (#10016)
    View User HP: 0
